@startuml hand-off-session-architecture

title hand_off_session — 模块架构 (baton 接力 5 大块)

' 节点名用日常术语优先,内部 module 名 / 函数名 / LOC / commit / REVIEW 引用见 INDEX

package "入口" as L1 {
  [MCP 入口 + 入口拦截\n(deny external)] as Entry
}

package "tool 实现" as L2 {
  [hand_off facade\n(参数解析 + cwd 反查 + adopt loop)] as Handler
  [plan resolve 业务层\n(读 plan + 校验 + 构造 cold start prompt)] as Impl
  [adopt context block\n(注入接管的 team 列表到 spawn prompt)] as AdoptCtx
}

package "起新 session" as L3 {
  [spawn 控制器\n(handOffMode=true 跳防御 + 不写 spawn-link)] as Spawn
  [adapter + SDK 子进程\n(claude / codex)] as Adapter
}

package "baton 收尾" as L4 {
  [baton 收尾流程\n(phase 1 关 teammate + phase 2 归档 caller)] as Baton
}

package "持久层 + 联动" as L5 {
  [4 张数据表\n(会话 / 团队 / 任务)] as Repos
  [会话管理器 + 事件总线] as SM
  folder "plan 文件 + worktree" as Fs
}

' ─── 调用链 ───

Entry --> Handler : 通过白名单后进 facade
Handler --> Repos : 反查 caller cwd
Handler --> Impl : plan-driven 模式调 plan resolve

alt plan-driven (传 plan_id)
  Impl --> Fs : 按 fallback 链找 plan 文件
  Impl --> Handler : 返 plan 元数据 + cold start prompt
else generic (无 plan_id)
  Handler --> Handler : 直接构造 generic 上下文
end

Handler --> Spawn : 起新 SDK session
Spawn --> Adapter : claude / codex adapter
Adapter --> SM : upsert 新 session + emit event

Handler --> Repos : 改 task ownership (clear / preserve / skip 三态)

opt adopt_teammates=true (接管 caller 同 team)
  Handler --> Repos : 转交 lead 角色 (swapLead 逐 team)
  Handler --> AdoptCtx : 构造 adopt block 注入 spawn prompt
end

Handler --> Baton : runBatonCleanup
Baton --> SM : phase 1 关 teammate (excludeSessionIds={newSid})
Baton --> Repos : phase 2 归档 caller session
Baton --> Handler : 返 cleanup 结果
Handler --> Entry : ok({sessionId, archived, adopted, taskReassignment, ...})

' ─── 关键不变量 ───

note bottom of Spawn
  关键不变量:
  - handOffMode=true → 跳 spawn-guards 三道防御 + 永不写 spawn-link
  - hand-off 是平级接力 (不是派遣关系),SessionList 不挂 teammate badge
end note

note bottom of Baton
  与 archive_plan 共享 baton 流程(同 helper)
  失败兜底见 hand-off-session-state-machine 图
end note

@enduml
